 <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4" id="why-choose-1-on-1-online-lessons">Why Choose 1-on-1 Online Lessons?</h2>

 <ContextualCTA text="Affordable lessons don't have to mean low quality. Check out See Guru's vetted tutor list." />
 <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">Learning English one-on-one with a real tutor is one of the fastest ways to improve. Unlike group classes where you share the teacher's attention, 1-on-1 lessons are built entirely around you.</p>
 <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">With online platforms, you get:</p>
 <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 text-neutral-300 space-y-2">
 <li><strong>Personalized feedback</strong> on your pronunciation, grammar, and vocabulary choices</li>
 <li><strong>Flexible scheduling</strong> to fit lessons around your job, school, or daily routine</li>
 <li><strong>Lower cost</strong> than traditional language schools since you pay only for teaching time</li>
 <li><strong>Access to native speakers</strong> from around the world without traveling</li>
 </ul>
 <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-4">The best part? You do not need to spend $50 per hour to get excellent results. Many quality tutors charge between $3 and $15 per lesson.</p>

